```sql
-- 01_customer_channel_attribution.sql
WITH customer_latest_attribution AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) AS rn
  FROM customer_channels
)
SELECT 
  customer_id,
  channel
FROM customer_latest_attribution
WHERE rn = 1
```

```sql
-- 02_transaction_enrichment.sql
WITH customer_latest_attribution AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) AS rn
  FROM customer_channels
),
customer_channels_deduped AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel
  FROM customer_latest_attribution
  WHERE rn = 1
)
SELECT 
  t.transaction_id,
  t.customer_id,
  t.store_id,
  t.amount,
  t.transaction_date,
  COALESCE(ccd.channel, 'unattributed') AS channel,
  COALESCE(s.city, 'unknown') AS city
FROM transactions t
LEFT JOIN customer_channels_deduped ccd ON t.customer_id = ccd.customer_id
LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
```

```sql
-- 03_revenue_by_attribution_channel.sql
WITH customer_latest_attribution AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) AS rn
  FROM customer_channels
),
customer_channels_deduped AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel
  FROM customer_latest_attribution
  WHERE rn = 1
),
transaction_enriched AS (
  SELECT 
    t.customer_id,
    t.amount,
    COALESCE(ccd.channel, 'unattributed') AS channel,
    COALESCE(s.city, 'unknown') AS city
  FROM transactions t
  LEFT JOIN customer_channels_deduped ccd ON t.customer_id = ccd.customer_id
  LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
)
SELECT 
  channel,
  city,
  SUM(amount) AS total_revenue,
  COUNT(*) AS transaction_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT customer_id) AS unique_customers
FROM transaction_enriched
GROUP BY channel, city
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC, channel, city
